WEBVTT

01:50.270 --> 01:53.930
[Love Between Lines]

01:54.350 --> 01:56.820
[Episode 10]

01:58.360 --> 02:00.880
How am I supposed to explain to Zhao

02:00.900 --> 02:02.570
that I'm moving back?

02:16.180 --> 02:16.950
Xiu,

02:16.970 --> 02:18.400
help me finish the leftover cake

02:18.400 --> 02:19.560
from my shop.

02:24.190 --> 02:24.750
Zhao,

02:25.329 --> 02:27.660
I'm moving back to my old place
in the lane.

02:28.820 --> 02:30.380
I've already discussed it with my boss.

02:30.380 --> 02:32.640
We're in the home stretch of the project,

02:32.820 --> 02:35.680
so it's more convenient for work
if we share a place.

02:38.030 --> 02:39.140
That makes sense. I'd be worried

02:39.140 --> 02:40.310
if you lived alone.

02:40.579 --> 02:41.630
What did you say?

02:43.140 --> 02:44.910
I said this room is too small.

02:45.230 --> 02:46.820
It's really not convenient for you
to live here.

02:46.820 --> 02:48.280
Moving back is a good idea.

02:51.980 --> 02:53.240
Let me help you pack up.

02:58.660 --> 03:00.310
It really isn't convenient.

03:05.540 --> 03:07.070
I'll take you back to the lane later.

03:07.070 --> 03:08.330
You have so much stuff.

03:08.420 --> 03:09.100
No need.

03:09.100 --> 03:10.950
My boss lent me his car.

03:12.350 --> 03:14.810
You're on such good terms with
your boss now?

03:15.260 --> 03:15.950
Not really.

03:15.950 --> 03:17.190
I just earned it

03:17.190 --> 03:18.630
by working overtime.

03:19.380 --> 03:20.100
Alright.

04:08.190 --> 04:08.820
Mr. Xiao.

04:09.420 --> 04:11.280
You just parked my car on the street?

04:11.280 --> 04:13.280
I just finished moving everything.

04:13.660 --> 04:15.580
I'll go park it in the lot now.

04:21.700 --> 04:22.230
Mr. Xiao,

04:22.780 --> 04:23.900
I can go by myself.

04:24.110 --> 04:26.430
It's just a short walk.
You don't need to come with me.

04:26.430 --> 04:28.290
But it's still a bit of a distance.

04:35.900 --> 04:36.670
Mr. Xiao,

04:36.670 --> 04:38.750
do we really have to wash the car
at this hour?

04:38.750 --> 04:40.220
It's just a bit of mud.

04:40.430 --> 04:41.760
And it's still raining.

04:43.900 --> 04:45.550
I've checked the weather forecast.

04:45.550 --> 04:48.150
The rain will stop
by the time the car is washed.

04:52.780 --> 04:53.380
It's okay.

04:53.550 --> 04:55.280
I can manage with only one hand.

05:00.260 --> 05:01.550
Then... then go ahead and wash it.

05:01.550 --> 05:03.340
I'll go back and unpack.

05:03.870 --> 05:04.380
Okay.

05:31.820 --> 05:32.950
You left something?

05:33.430 --> 05:34.190
Yes, yes.

05:34.190 --> 05:35.310
I left my conscience behind.

05:35.310 --> 05:36.430
Here, give it to me.

05:39.830 --> 05:41.030
You go sit over there.

05:57.090 --> 06:02.950
♪ Life lays out the outline of my scenes ♪

06:04.190 --> 06:07.660
♪ The last act
was a monologue in a dream ♪

06:08.860 --> 06:12.630
♪ And in the next,
I wander through the city's noise ♪

06:13.790 --> 06:16.860
♪ So many arrivals
that turned out to be nothing ♪

06:18.440 --> 06:22.090
♪ I'm counting the beats of the clock ♪

06:23.150 --> 06:26.950
♪ I can't tell which platform
is for leaving or returning ♪

06:26.700 --> 06:27.990
When you lost your job earlier,

06:27.820 --> 06:32.090
♪ Until you walk toward me ♪

06:27.990 --> 06:29.070
you shouldn't have worried at all.

06:29.070 --> 06:31.400
Look at you, you're great at washing cars.

06:32.950 --> 06:33.820
Mr. Xiao,

06:33.520 --> 06:37.100
♪ And my breath softens ♪

06:33.950 --> 06:36.310
I can do even better as a designer!

06:37.070 --> 06:37.750
Fine.

06:38.140 --> 06:39.580
Then tomorrow night, no car washing.

06:38.620 --> 06:43.000
♪ I forget every absurd line ♪

06:39.780 --> 06:41.040
Draw designs instead.

06:43.770 --> 06:47.750
♪ Because of you ♪

06:45.220 --> 06:46.630
These are blueprints I've just revised.

06:46.630 --> 06:47.580
If these get ruined,

06:47.580 --> 06:48.540
you'll be responsible.

06:48.540 --> 06:55.310
♪ So you're beside the story
written by fate ♪

06:50.110 --> 06:50.950
Wash the car properly.

06:50.950 --> 06:52.280
I'm going to get a drink.

06:54.340 --> 06:55.460
My hands are all wet,

06:55.460 --> 06:57.190
and you're making me hold it...

06:57.850 --> 06:59.300
♪ Oh, ok ♪

07:00.300 --> 07:01.720
♪ Oh, ok ♪

07:01.260 --> 07:02.430
You're playing me?

07:02.320 --> 07:03.580
♪ Oh, ok ♪

07:03.070 --> 07:03.950
You still want water?

07:03.950 --> 07:04.670
I'll give you some water.

07:04.620 --> 07:06.620
♪ Oh, ok ♪

07:04.670 --> 07:06.110
Drink your fill! Drink!

07:06.970 --> 07:10.080
♪ Oh, ok, my love ♪

07:11.010 --> 07:14.870
♪ It turns out you're my exception ♪

07:25.260 --> 07:26.460
What's wrong, Hu Xiu?

07:26.460 --> 07:28.120
Didn't sleep well last night?

07:28.460 --> 07:29.340
Yeah.

07:29.630 --> 07:30.260
Moving

07:30.260 --> 07:31.190
is exhausting.

07:33.460 --> 07:33.950
Here.

07:35.340 --> 07:36.940
A little pick-me-up for you.

07:37.360 --> 07:39.690
I remember you love these konjac jellies.

07:40.430 --> 07:42.030
Moving is quite exhausting.

07:46.220 --> 07:47.430
Especially when you have

07:47.430 --> 07:51.230
a roommate who doesn't understand
the meaning of "peace and quiet."

07:57.240 --> 07:58.150
Ms. Hu,

07:58.220 --> 08:00.510
why haven't I seen you at the café lately?

08:01.920 --> 08:03.600
I've already moved.

08:06.670 --> 08:07.670
Why?

08:07.950 --> 08:09.480
Is it because of that video?

08:09.870 --> 08:10.820
Video?

08:12.000 --> 08:13.150
What video?

08:27.190 --> 08:27.750
Okay.

08:28.400 --> 08:30.330
I'll communicate with them again.

08:30.550 --> 08:31.080
Goodbye.

08:32.620 --> 08:33.270
Mr. Xiao.

08:35.390 --> 08:36.789
I'd like to leave two hours early

08:36.789 --> 08:37.700
today.

08:38.070 --> 08:38.700
How about

08:38.700 --> 08:40.390
you take a taxi home tonight?

08:41.429 --> 08:42.289
What happened?

08:42.860 --> 08:43.500
It's Zhao,

08:43.620 --> 08:45.430
my friend who runs the café.

08:45.700 --> 08:47.070
She got into a fight at the club last time

08:47.070 --> 08:48.520
and got herself into some trouble.

08:48.520 --> 08:50.510
And I moved out
without knowing anything about it.

08:50.510 --> 08:52.510
I want to go back to the café for a bit.

08:53.430 --> 08:53.950
Okay.

08:54.910 --> 08:55.460
Wait.

08:56.620 --> 08:57.950
You have my keys, right?

08:58.250 --> 08:59.090
Take my car.

09:00.860 --> 09:01.990
Thank you, Mr. Xiao.

09:10.370 --> 09:12.030
Ms. Zhao, sorry to bother you.

09:14.070 --> 09:15.130
What's the matter?

09:17.220 --> 09:18.030
Ms. Zhao,

09:18.160 --> 09:19.680
I'm just here to notify you

09:19.740 --> 09:21.740
that next quarter, your shop's rent

09:22.100 --> 09:24.430
will be raised according to regulations.

09:24.820 --> 09:25.860
No, that's not right.

09:25.860 --> 09:27.800
I've already discussed this
with the industrial park management.

09:27.800 --> 09:29.670
I provide discounted coffee
in exchange for

09:29.670 --> 09:30.550
keeping the rent the same.

09:30.550 --> 09:31.810
Why the sudden change?

09:31.980 --> 09:33.070
Well...

09:33.340 --> 09:35.340
All those previous business arrangements

09:35.340 --> 09:36.980
are no longer valid.

09:40.340 --> 09:41.820
Did something happen?

09:42.700 --> 09:43.430
Ms. Zhao,

09:44.030 --> 09:46.390
your shop has been reported
for mixed commercial and residential use.

09:46.390 --> 09:46.950
We can't

09:46.950 --> 09:48.680
just ignore this kind of thing.

09:48.740 --> 09:50.100
After the leadership found out,

09:50.100 --> 09:52.390
they stopped
all previous cooperation with you.

09:52.390 --> 09:52.990
That's why

09:53.460 --> 09:55.790
they sent me here to verify the situation.

09:55.820 --> 09:58.980
But I specifically consulted with
the property management about this.

09:58.980 --> 10:00.030
My second-floor loft

10:00.030 --> 10:01.460
isn't open to the public.

10:01.460 --> 10:03.190
They said short-term residence
wasn't a problem.

10:03.190 --> 10:04.550
Yeah, that's true.

10:04.550 --> 10:06.460
Normally, we wouldn't be
so strict about it.

10:06.460 --> 10:07.260
But you see...

10:07.430 --> 10:08.760
someone filed a report,

10:08.820 --> 10:10.620
so we have to take action, right?

10:13.520 --> 10:13.980
Well,

10:13.980 --> 10:15.700
can you tell me who reported it?

10:15.700 --> 10:17.500
I'd like to discuss it with them.

10:17.550 --> 10:18.340
Well...

10:18.620 --> 10:21.030
I'm afraid
I can't disclose that information.

10:21.030 --> 10:21.860
Sorry about that.

10:21.860 --> 10:22.700
I found out.

10:23.900 --> 10:25.630
It was all Qian Jinxin's doing.

10:51.390 --> 10:52.100
Ms. Zhao,

10:52.310 --> 10:54.100
I've sent you the complete video.

10:54.100 --> 10:54.950
Maybe it'll help.

10:54.950 --> 10:55.910
You didn't know all along

10:55.910 --> 10:59.170
that your bestie was
flirting with another actor, did you?

11:00.890 --> 11:02.190
He hit a woman.

11:02.190 --> 11:02.980
He hit a woman?

11:02.980 --> 11:03.740
Shameless!

11:15.620 --> 11:16.270
I'm the owner

11:16.270 --> 11:17.550
of the Regard Café.

11:17.700 --> 11:19.310
Here's what really happened

11:19.310 --> 11:20.340
that day

11:20.670 --> 11:22.470
at the murder mystery game club.

11:29.390 --> 11:32.030
The most beautiful café owner in the world—

11:32.420 --> 11:34.150
do you still have coffee?

11:37.580 --> 11:39.670
There's only one cup of cold coffee left,

11:39.670 --> 11:41.330
and the latte art is terrible.

11:41.600 --> 11:43.240
If you don't mind,

11:43.460 --> 11:44.460
it's on the house.

11:44.690 --> 11:48.990
♪ Under the streetlight,
I grow increasingly weary ♪

11:45.770 --> 11:46.530
I don't mind.

11:51.140 --> 11:55.980
♪ A few specks of dust
drift by in the wind ♪

11:58.080 --> 12:02.240
♪ The girl who once
basked in the sunlight ♪

12:03.100 --> 12:06.020
♪ Where did she go to play? ♪

12:03.860 --> 12:05.050
Xiu, I'm sorry.

12:06.460 --> 12:09.430
♪ I don't understand either ♪

12:07.310 --> 12:10.110
I should've explained everything
to you earlier.

12:11.150 --> 12:12.700
I thought

12:11.670 --> 12:15.500
♪ Flicking through old chat logs ♪

12:13.030 --> 12:15.030
Wang's project had fallen through,

12:15.270 --> 12:16.070
and if I had

12:16.070 --> 12:17.980
spoken badly about Qian Jinxin online
at that time,

12:17.750 --> 12:22.630
♪ I just realized the replies
were somewhat delayed ♪

12:18.670 --> 12:21.330
I might not have been able to
keep this shop open.

12:21.460 --> 12:22.620
He's still building his business,

12:22.620 --> 12:23.310
so...

12:23.770 --> 12:29.760
♪ At the crossroads of choices,
amidst the bustling crowd ♪

12:25.430 --> 12:26.670
I didn't know what to do.

12:26.670 --> 12:28.100
I thought I'd wait
until all this blew over,

12:28.100 --> 12:28.630
then I...

12:31.000 --> 12:38.270
♪ Who hasn't paid the price
and still fallen short? ♪

12:36.950 --> 12:37.670
Zhao,

12:38.070 --> 12:39.620
you don't need to apologize,

12:38.290 --> 12:42.840
♪ Stand with me tonight,
look at the starlight ♪

12:39.620 --> 12:42.480
and you don't need to
explain anything to me either.

12:43.650 --> 12:49.690
♪ Even if we're always
pushed aside by reality ♪

12:43.700 --> 12:46.230
But what if Qian Jinxin
causes trouble again?

12:47.070 --> 12:47.800
I don't care.

12:48.790 --> 12:50.570
I'm going to fight back right now.

12:50.570 --> 12:56.780
♪ I know the dark clouds will still come ♪

12:56.220 --> 12:56.860
Zhao.

12:57.320 --> 13:05.670
♪ But in this world,
there will always be someone ♪

12:58.310 --> 12:59.110
I support you.

12:59.460 --> 13:01.590
I'll support you no matter what you do.

13:03.910 --> 13:06.390
Then you have to support me
like this forever.

13:06.390 --> 13:09.670
♪ Who looks forward
with the same hope as me ♪

13:07.460 --> 13:08.500
The coffee spilled.

13:08.500 --> 13:09.790
Mop the floor.

13:10.100 --> 13:11.500
You're ordering me around?

13:11.500 --> 13:12.270
I'll mop it. I'll mop it.

13:12.270 --> 13:13.600
My fault. It's my fault.

13:13.620 --> 13:14.980
Such expensive coffee—

13:14.980 --> 13:16.070
what a waste.

13:16.600 --> 13:17.060
Well...

13:17.520 --> 13:18.430
Drink it then.

13:21.510 --> 13:23.220
I'll drink it. I'll really drink it.

13:23.220 --> 13:23.800
I'll drink.

13:23.800 --> 13:24.370
Go ahead.

13:25.430 --> 13:26.160
Qian Jinxin,

13:26.500 --> 13:27.800
I just transferred you here,

13:27.800 --> 13:29.150
and you've already caused
such a huge mess!

13:29.150 --> 13:30.150
What were you thinking?

13:30.150 --> 13:30.700
Boss,

13:31.030 --> 13:32.220
I'm innocent.

13:32.340 --> 13:34.700
It was those two girls
who were giving me trouble.

13:34.700 --> 13:35.270
Enough!

13:35.670 --> 13:37.230
There's a complete video online.

13:37.230 --> 13:38.430
Stop making excuses!

13:38.430 --> 13:39.620
Because of you alone,

13:39.620 --> 13:41.860
the reputation of the entire
industrial park staff has been tarnished!

13:41.860 --> 13:43.030
The impact is terrible!

13:43.030 --> 13:43.580
Come to my office

13:43.580 --> 13:44.340
first thing tomorrow morning!

13:44.340 --> 13:45.550
Boss, I was wrong.

13:45.550 --> 13:46.100
Boss...

14:09.750 --> 14:11.230
After you started sharing
an apartment with your boss,

14:11.230 --> 14:12.750
you're sharing a car too?

14:13.500 --> 14:14.900
Things between him and me

14:14.980 --> 14:16.860
are rather complicated.

14:17.150 --> 14:20.150
Once things get complicated,
they become dangerous.

14:23.790 --> 14:24.790
What does he want?

14:26.050 --> 14:27.650
Qian Jinxin, are you crazy?

14:27.820 --> 14:28.860
If you won't let me live in peace,

14:28.860 --> 14:30.280
neither of you will have peace!

14:30.280 --> 14:31.280
Xiu, be careful.

14:31.310 --> 14:31.950
It's okay.

14:58.070 --> 14:59.190
Stop right there!

15:05.930 --> 15:06.860
Pei Zhen?

15:08.420 --> 15:08.990
Xiu,

15:09.310 --> 15:10.970
we need to call the police now.

15:11.340 --> 15:18.650
[For plot purposes only—do not imitate]

15:54.610 --> 15:56.000
How did you even drive like that?

15:56.000 --> 15:57.300
You've got a death wish?

15:57.300 --> 15:58.900
Do you even know how to drive?

16:08.310 --> 16:08.670
Wait...

16:08.670 --> 16:09.980
W-What do you want?

16:12.390 --> 16:13.590
I've got a death wish.

16:13.670 --> 16:15.270
Go ahead and call the police.

16:16.810 --> 16:17.210
You...

16:19.550 --> 16:20.670
Are you nuts?

16:27.030 --> 16:27.580
Mr. Pei.

16:27.950 --> 16:28.620
Ms. Hu.

16:28.980 --> 16:30.430
I'm really sorry about tonight.

16:30.430 --> 16:31.390
It all happened so suddenly,

16:31.390 --> 16:31.950
and I...

16:31.950 --> 16:33.480
didn't see your car coming.

16:33.860 --> 16:34.430
It's okay.

16:34.430 --> 16:36.670
It wasn't your fault that the car got hit.

16:36.670 --> 16:39.500
Actually, you didn't need to
chase after him.

16:41.040 --> 16:42.270
I wasn't thinking much at that moment.

16:42.270 --> 16:43.460
I saw him running away,

16:43.460 --> 16:45.730
so I thought I'd take a shortcut
to stop him.

16:45.730 --> 16:47.550
Who knew he would turn around right then?

16:47.550 --> 16:48.950
Now that I think about it,

16:48.980 --> 16:50.220
it was pretty scary.

16:52.550 --> 16:53.790
Last time at the property site,

16:53.790 --> 16:55.850
did I put you in a difficult position?

16:56.390 --> 17:00.340
Mr. Xiao wouldn't make things difficult
for someone over such a small matter.

17:00.340 --> 17:01.860
I just think it's a pity.

17:02.100 --> 17:04.440
If our two companies weren't competitors,

17:04.440 --> 17:06.569
you and I could have been good friends.

17:07.430 --> 17:08.670
It seems we need to win

17:08.670 --> 17:10.530
the Design Competition quickly.

17:11.430 --> 17:12.980
He won't lose either.

17:18.530 --> 17:19.480
All done, Xiu.

17:19.980 --> 17:21.150
The police said

17:21.150 --> 17:23.220
that administrative penalties
for him and for us are inevitable.

17:23.220 --> 17:24.260
As for criminal liability,

17:24.260 --> 17:25.650
they'll investigate further.

17:25.650 --> 17:26.589
If they need our cooperation,

17:26.589 --> 17:27.720
they'll contact us.

17:29.460 --> 17:30.720
You're Mr. Pei, right?

17:30.780 --> 17:32.190
Thank you so much for today.

17:32.190 --> 17:33.500
-Nice to meet you.
-Sorry for the trouble.

17:33.500 --> 17:34.830
I just heard from the officer

17:34.830 --> 17:36.740
that vehicle damage claims are
quite complicated,

17:36.740 --> 17:38.150
and it seems you need some kind of
liability determination report...

17:38.150 --> 17:38.980
It's fine.

17:39.030 --> 17:40.050
My assistant is coming.

17:40.050 --> 17:41.390
I'll have him take care of it.

17:41.390 --> 17:41.980
Okay.

17:42.390 --> 17:43.060
Then,

17:43.060 --> 17:44.350
let's exchange contact info.

17:44.350 --> 17:44.540
Sure.

17:44.540 --> 17:46.110
If you need my help later,

17:46.110 --> 17:46.910
just contact me anytime.

17:46.910 --> 17:48.040
I'll scan your code.

17:48.840 --> 17:50.440
I was the one driving the car.

17:50.540 --> 17:51.430
But you were helping me with my situation,

17:51.430 --> 17:53.830
so of course I should take responsibility.

17:54.910 --> 17:56.350
Mr. Pei, so that's settled then.

17:56.350 --> 17:58.150
If anything comes up later,
just contact me directly.

17:58.150 --> 17:58.680
Alright.

17:58.980 --> 18:00.040
We'll be going now.

18:00.300 --> 18:00.870
Bye-bye, Ms. Hu.

18:00.870 --> 18:01.430
Bye-bye.

18:14.870 --> 18:15.350
Mr. Pei.

18:15.990 --> 18:16.870
Are you alright?

18:16.870 --> 18:17.400
I'm fine.

18:17.910 --> 18:19.630
Just finished dealing with the penalty.

18:19.630 --> 18:20.500
But I don't understand—

18:20.500 --> 18:21.670
why did you waste your time

18:21.670 --> 18:22.700
helping them?

18:26.220 --> 18:28.110
That's Xiao Zhiyu's car, isn't it?

18:28.110 --> 18:28.910
That's right.

18:29.130 --> 18:31.190
It's hard not to be curious, isn't it?

18:34.980 --> 18:37.780
You have to play the long game
to catch the big fish.

18:38.460 --> 18:39.460
What about your car?

18:39.460 --> 18:40.740
Should I take it in for repairs first

18:40.740 --> 18:42.110
and then deal with that guy, or...

18:42.110 --> 18:43.440
Just get rid of it for me.

18:50.980 --> 18:52.900
A defective product is
a defective product.

18:52.900 --> 18:55.430
It'll still be defective,
even if it's fixed.

19:11.430 --> 19:12.060
Mr. Xiao,

19:12.500 --> 19:13.700
you're still up?

19:14.460 --> 19:15.670
You startled me.

19:16.060 --> 19:17.390
If I could use this hand properly,

19:17.390 --> 19:20.250
I wouldn't be sitting here all night
doing nothing.

19:22.350 --> 19:23.390
I'm sorry.

19:23.910 --> 19:24.950
I...

19:26.150 --> 19:28.680
got held up
helping my friend with something.

19:29.020 --> 19:30.430
I can work now.

19:41.060 --> 19:42.260
Something happened?

19:46.260 --> 19:46.980
Mr. Xiao.

19:48.260 --> 19:49.150
Actually...

19:49.950 --> 19:51.020
just now...

19:51.260 --> 19:52.950
I almost crashed your car.

19:54.080 --> 19:54.840
Are you okay?

19:57.800 --> 19:58.430
But

19:58.450 --> 19:59.730
I ran into Mr. Pei.

20:04.870 --> 20:06.730
That's basically what happened.

20:07.350 --> 20:09.300
I don't know
why it was such a coincidence,

20:09.300 --> 20:11.230
but I thought I should let you know.

20:11.950 --> 20:12.500
Don't worry.

20:12.500 --> 20:14.560
I didn't talk about work with Mr. Pei.

20:14.590 --> 20:16.060
If there's anything
that needs to be handled later,

20:16.060 --> 20:17.520
I'll have Zhao take care of it
to avoid anything

20:17.520 --> 20:18.220
that could cause misunderstandings.

20:18.220 --> 20:19.020
Next time,

20:19.840 --> 20:22.570
contact the car owner first
if anything happens.

20:25.350 --> 20:26.460
I mean,

20:27.220 --> 20:28.220
contact me first.

20:30.780 --> 20:31.500
Got it.

20:36.740 --> 20:38.670
We're not continuing with the drawings?

20:38.670 --> 20:39.780
Get some rest.

21:39.850 --> 21:40.680
Hello, Zhao.

21:41.950 --> 21:42.500
Hello, Xiu.

21:42.500 --> 21:45.100
Check the industrial park's
announcement now.

21:45.100 --> 21:45.870
You know what?

21:45.870 --> 21:47.110
Early this morning,

21:47.110 --> 21:50.310
the park's leadership was waiting for me
at the entrance.

21:50.910 --> 21:52.710
Did they give you trouble again?

21:53.190 --> 21:54.110
No.

21:54.500 --> 21:56.540
The leadership
personally apologized to me.

21:56.540 --> 21:59.300
They said my cooperation with the park
will continue as usual.

21:59.300 --> 22:00.220
And the rent

22:00.300 --> 22:01.980
won't increase at all.

22:02.950 --> 22:03.910
That's great!

22:04.570 --> 22:05.220
That's not all.

22:05.220 --> 22:06.480
Let me show you a video.

22:14.540 --> 22:15.980
Stop filming... Stop filming!

22:15.980 --> 22:16.830
Someone like you

22:16.830 --> 22:17.500
should have been kicked out long ago!

22:17.500 --> 22:17.910
Stop filming!

22:17.910 --> 22:18.540
That's right!

22:18.540 --> 22:19.300
Stop filming!

22:19.300 --> 22:20.910
I've already apologized!

22:21.500 --> 22:22.540
Shameless!

22:22.540 --> 22:22.870
Don't cover your face!

22:22.870 --> 22:24.470
Stop filming! Stop filming!

22:24.780 --> 22:25.630
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

22:25.630 --> 22:26.430
Stop filming!

22:28.980 --> 22:29.980
I asked around.

22:29.980 --> 22:31.780
Apparently, the owner of ME Club

22:31.780 --> 22:33.150
pressured the park management,

22:33.150 --> 22:33.830
firmly refusing to allow

22:33.830 --> 22:35.910
someone like Qian Jinxin
to manage the park.

22:35.910 --> 22:37.780
So he was fired immediately.

22:39.210 --> 22:40.820
The ME Club owner?

23:05.260 --> 23:06.590
Good morning, Mr. Xiao.

23:06.590 --> 23:07.720
Breakfast is ready.

23:13.820 --> 23:15.260
That's what we didn't finish last night.

23:15.260 --> 23:17.060
Let's continue this afternoon.

23:17.220 --> 23:17.950
Also,

23:18.630 --> 23:19.630
this bowl of porridge—

23:19.630 --> 23:21.360
I bought it as a thank-you gift.

23:24.020 --> 23:25.430
You helped out with

23:25.690 --> 23:27.820
the vendors' protest too, didn't you?

23:28.780 --> 23:30.110
I just wanted to get justice

23:30.110 --> 23:31.240
for my injured hand.

23:32.670 --> 23:33.470
I understand.

23:34.300 --> 23:35.100
I understand.

23:39.980 --> 23:40.840
What are these?

23:41.590 --> 23:42.350
Onion bulbs.

23:43.020 --> 23:44.260
I want to grow green onions.

23:44.260 --> 23:45.630
If we're cooking at home,

23:45.630 --> 23:46.980
how can we not have green onions?

23:46.980 --> 23:47.540
Real onions.

23:47.540 --> 23:47.980
No need.

23:47.980 --> 23:49.240
Your delivery is here!

23:50.150 --> 23:50.700
Coming!

23:53.330 --> 23:54.220
Hello, your flowers.

23:54.220 --> 23:55.150
Thank you.

23:55.150 --> 23:55.910
Have a nice day.

23:55.910 --> 23:56.780
You too.

23:59.220 --> 24:00.020
Who sent them?

24:00.780 --> 24:01.980
I bought them myself.

24:04.230 --> 24:05.500
Is it also a thank-you gift for me?

24:05.500 --> 24:06.260
No.

24:09.590 --> 24:10.260
Of course, Mr. Xiao,

24:10.260 --> 24:11.390
if you like them,

24:11.910 --> 24:13.110
I can share half with you.

24:13.110 --> 24:13.740
No need.

24:18.780 --> 24:19.870
Another delivery?

24:21.220 --> 24:21.910
Xiu?

24:23.360 --> 24:24.510
Xiu, open the door.

24:24.830 --> 24:25.500
It's my dad.

24:25.830 --> 24:26.460
My dad is here.

24:26.460 --> 24:27.660
Quick, quick, hurry!

24:30.010 --> 24:30.650
Xiu?

24:40.020 --> 24:41.220
Bathroom! Bathroom!

24:46.950 --> 24:47.500
Dad!

24:47.830 --> 24:48.870
What were you doing?

24:48.870 --> 24:49.740
I've been knocking forever,
and you didn't answer.

24:49.740 --> 24:51.830
I... I was listening to music.

24:51.830 --> 24:53.630
I was... I was dancing in my room.

24:54.510 --> 24:55.230
Dancing.

24:56.260 --> 24:57.350
Why did you come so suddenly

24:57.350 --> 24:58.980
without telling me first?

24:59.910 --> 25:02.510
Do I... do I have to report to you
before coming?

25:02.830 --> 25:04.260
I... I guess not.

25:05.500 --> 25:06.780
I made some food for you.

25:06.780 --> 25:08.430
Get a couple of bowls and dish it out.

25:08.430 --> 25:09.060
Okay.

25:11.110 --> 25:12.710
Why is there a new table here?

25:13.500 --> 25:14.780
I needed it for work,

25:14.780 --> 25:15.840
so I just bought it.

25:20.830 --> 25:21.460
Xiu.

25:21.910 --> 25:22.840
Your mother and I

25:22.880 --> 25:24.410
came all this way
to bring you those two bottles of baijiu.

25:24.410 --> 25:26.270
You didn't give them to your boss?

25:28.190 --> 25:30.630
Dad, it'd be a waste
to give them to my boss.

25:30.950 --> 25:31.500
He...

25:31.670 --> 25:33.350
He has high blood pressure,
high blood sugar, and high cholesterol—

25:33.350 --> 25:34.670
he can't even have a sip of alcohol.

25:34.670 --> 25:36.150
If I eagerly gave him baijiu,

25:36.150 --> 25:38.220
w-wouldn't that show I'm clueless?

25:39.500 --> 25:41.150
T-That many health problems?

25:41.150 --> 25:42.880
You should've told me earlier.

25:43.150 --> 25:44.780
Dad, you don't need to bring me food.

25:44.780 --> 25:45.510
I think I

25:45.540 --> 25:47.060
can take care of myself.

25:47.350 --> 25:48.060
Before you

25:48.060 --> 25:49.430
say things like that next time,

25:49.430 --> 25:50.590
put away this junk food

25:50.590 --> 25:51.290
first.

25:51.310 --> 25:51.860
It's the middle of the day.

25:51.860 --> 25:53.460
Why are you having porridge?

25:53.540 --> 25:55.400
I-It's leftover from breakfast.

25:56.880 --> 25:58.800
Dad, don't worry about this.

25:58.870 --> 26:00.260
I still have

26:00.260 --> 26:02.190
a lot of work to do after I eat.

26:02.670 --> 26:03.590
If I can't

26:03.590 --> 26:04.950
complete my work on time,

26:04.950 --> 26:06.430
no amount of gift-giving will help,

26:06.430 --> 26:06.950
right?

26:07.390 --> 26:08.150
Right, right.

26:08.150 --> 26:09.870
Let me walk you out to get a taxi.

26:09.870 --> 26:10.690
Let's go. Let's go.

26:10.690 --> 26:11.020
Okay, okay.

26:11.020 --> 26:12.260
I'm really busy today, Dad.

26:12.260 --> 26:12.980
Okay, okay.

26:14.910 --> 26:15.740
Wait, no rush.

26:18.240 --> 26:19.300
What's that sound?

26:19.540 --> 26:21.400
Maybe Dazhong is taking a shower!

26:23.430 --> 26:25.190
His bathroom and our living room

26:25.190 --> 26:26.920
are only separated by one wall.

26:27.300 --> 26:28.630
No, the sound seems to be coming from
over there...

26:28.630 --> 26:29.540
That's empty.

26:29.540 --> 26:31.260
How could anyone be there, Dad?

26:31.260 --> 26:32.740
Let me walk you out. Put your shoes on.

26:32.740 --> 26:33.190
Okay.

26:33.430 --> 26:34.060
Let me help you.

26:34.060 --> 26:34.780
Okay, okay.

26:35.780 --> 26:36.260
This foot.

26:36.260 --> 26:36.910
Alright, that's it.

26:36.910 --> 26:37.190
Be careful with your leg.

26:37.190 --> 26:37.950
Go on with your work.

26:37.950 --> 26:39.020
I'll walk you downstairs, Dad.

26:39.020 --> 26:39.460
No need, no need.

26:39.460 --> 26:39.950
Let me walk you...

26:39.950 --> 26:41.300
Just focus on your work.

26:41.300 --> 26:41.830
Don't let me hold you up.

26:41.830 --> 26:42.300
Okay.

26:42.390 --> 26:42.870
Bye.

26:42.870 --> 26:44.390
I'll let you know when I'm free.

26:44.390 --> 26:44.920
Alright!

26:45.260 --> 26:46.690
Be careful going downstairs!

26:46.690 --> 26:47.170
Okay.

26:47.780 --> 26:48.310
Bye-bye!

26:48.460 --> 26:49.190
Bye-bye!

27:00.990 --> 27:02.050
What are you doing?

27:03.590 --> 27:04.260
Mr. Xiao,

27:04.540 --> 27:05.630
I'm really sorry.

27:06.780 --> 27:07.780
It happened so suddenly.

27:07.780 --> 27:09.110
I had no choice.

27:09.340 --> 27:10.540
But I promise you—

27:10.590 --> 27:11.540
three times max!

27:11.780 --> 27:12.870
Three times max?

27:13.390 --> 27:15.720
So that means there's still one more time?

27:16.430 --> 27:17.430
Oh, you're right.

27:21.760 --> 27:24.120
You even took a shower in there?

27:28.060 --> 27:29.460
My thermos container...

27:30.350 --> 27:31.220
-Dad!
-Dad.

27:33.190 --> 27:34.150
U-Uncle, hello.

27:36.930 --> 27:38.690
How did you get in?

27:39.260 --> 27:41.660
Why didn't I hear anything?

27:42.610 --> 27:45.670
-You didn't close the door.
-You didn't close the door.

27:56.690 --> 27:57.210
Dad,

27:57.500 --> 27:58.670
this is Yu.

27:58.840 --> 28:00.100
You've met him before.

28:01.350 --> 28:02.060
I know.

28:02.390 --> 28:03.460
You're colleagues, right?

28:03.460 --> 28:03.910
Yes.

28:04.670 --> 28:05.700
You came today

28:06.660 --> 28:08.060
to pick up a contract too?

28:08.670 --> 28:09.870
Uncle, I came to get...

28:09.870 --> 28:11.930
Go upstairs and change your clothes.

28:12.430 --> 28:13.490
Don't catch a cold.

28:17.330 --> 28:17.860
Go ahead.

28:30.260 --> 28:32.220
You said you wanted to
focus on your career.

28:32.220 --> 28:33.110
You said there were many things

28:33.110 --> 28:34.110
more important than marriage.

28:34.110 --> 28:35.470
I actually believed you.

28:35.470 --> 28:37.400
You've forgotten about
Zhang Qiran already, haven't you?

28:37.400 --> 28:38.930
I'm not against you dating.

28:39.110 --> 28:39.460
But

28:39.460 --> 28:41.740
how long has it been since you broke off
your engagement with him?

28:41.740 --> 28:42.300
And now, you're...

28:42.300 --> 28:44.310
well, you're already living together?

28:44.310 --> 28:45.830
This lane isn't very big.

28:45.870 --> 28:46.630
People see everything.

28:46.630 --> 28:48.160
What will they think of you?

28:48.300 --> 28:50.560
Why should I care what others think of me?

28:51.680 --> 28:53.720
Yu and I are living together.

28:55.170 --> 28:56.970
But we're not in a relationship.

28:57.170 --> 28:58.410
He's my tenant.

28:58.560 --> 29:00.480
To be precise, we're roommates.

29:00.830 --> 29:01.350
Room...

29:01.670 --> 29:02.590
Roommates?

29:04.830 --> 29:06.540
Do your other colleagues

29:06.540 --> 29:08.670
know that you two are living together?

29:08.860 --> 29:10.730
Will they gossip about you?

29:13.830 --> 29:14.960
My other colleagues

29:15.030 --> 29:15.870
won't know.

29:17.060 --> 29:17.790
That's good.

29:18.290 --> 29:20.090
Because I've already resigned.

29:23.300 --> 29:24.160
That baijiu...

29:24.700 --> 29:26.260
I never gave it to Mr. Xu.

29:27.300 --> 29:28.260
I got rid of him long ago.

29:28.260 --> 29:29.500
He doesn't deserve it.

29:29.500 --> 29:30.190
Also,

29:30.190 --> 29:31.390
I didn't rent out the loft

29:31.390 --> 29:33.020
because he was struggling financially

29:33.020 --> 29:34.150
or needed help.

29:34.830 --> 29:35.670
I did it

29:35.870 --> 29:37.800
because I wanted the money myself.

29:39.100 --> 29:40.900
Yu and I are indeed colleagues.

29:42.590 --> 29:43.630
He's my boss,

29:44.590 --> 29:46.950
the founder of D Design Studio.

29:47.590 --> 29:48.630
W-W-What?

29:48.630 --> 29:49.910
What? Design what?

29:50.060 --> 29:50.430
What?

29:50.430 --> 29:51.980
D Design Studio.

29:53.950 --> 29:56.150
It's an architectural design company.

29:57.500 --> 29:59.870
Why architectural design again?

30:00.260 --> 30:01.190
No, you...

30:01.890 --> 30:03.830
You said you weren't happy at work,
so you quit,

30:03.830 --> 30:05.090
and I understand that.

30:05.150 --> 30:06.260
Shanghai is so big.

30:06.430 --> 30:07.630
There are so many companies.

30:07.630 --> 30:09.500
You have experience
as a general manager's assistant,

30:09.500 --> 30:09.980
right?

30:10.060 --> 30:11.980
You could work at any company you want.

30:11.980 --> 30:13.870
Why do you keep jumping around

30:13.870 --> 30:14.700
and ending up back in architecture again?

30:14.700 --> 30:16.460
I like architecture.

30:16.940 --> 30:20.090
♪ Fireworks scatter across the sky ♪

30:18.010 --> 30:18.490
Dad,

30:18.950 --> 30:20.540
if it weren't for this new job,

30:20.470 --> 30:24.600
♪ And the faint light in my eyes
fades with them ♪

30:20.540 --> 30:22.780
I wouldn't have moved on so quickly.

30:23.430 --> 30:25.830
What's good about working in architecture?

30:25.830 --> 30:27.540
It's hard, exhausting, and dangerous.

30:26.550 --> 30:29.850
♪ Just like the end of our story ♪

30:27.540 --> 30:29.190
You know all this.

30:29.460 --> 30:31.390
You said it when I was filling out
my college applications.

30:30.490 --> 30:32.380
♪ Who says ♪

30:31.390 --> 30:32.390
Exactly the same.

30:32.810 --> 30:37.180
♪ We meet just to say goodbye? ♪

30:33.910 --> 30:34.710
Yes, I said it.

30:35.190 --> 30:36.250
But did you listen?

30:37.220 --> 30:39.260
Back then, you even kept
your college applications from me

30:38.030 --> 30:42.970
♪ Who's to blame for a fate like this? ♪

30:39.260 --> 30:40.700
and insisted on studying architecture.

30:40.700 --> 30:41.830
When you graduated,

30:42.060 --> 30:44.190
because of this useless leg of mine...

30:44.220 --> 30:46.970
♪ Walking across ♪

30:45.910 --> 30:47.570
you didn't go abroad to study.

30:47.980 --> 30:49.910
Yet you chose to find a stable job
in Shanghai.

30:48.170 --> 30:53.720
♪ This hollow bridge of fate ♪

30:50.540 --> 30:52.070
I thought that was pretty good.

30:52.070 --> 30:54.070
Wasn't that a blessing in disguise?

30:54.190 --> 30:54.830
I thought that from then on,

30:54.830 --> 30:56.150
I wouldn't have to worry

30:55.000 --> 31:00.220
♪ If you can't see the other shore,
turn around ♪

30:56.150 --> 30:56.980
about you anymore.

30:56.980 --> 30:57.540
I never expected that today...

30:57.540 --> 30:58.700
So?

30:58.980 --> 30:59.740
Three years ago,

30:59.740 --> 31:01.060
I already missed one chance.

31:01.060 --> 31:02.430
I already gave up once.

31:01.830 --> 31:04.040
♪ Only a few stars shine ♪

31:02.430 --> 31:04.960
Do you want me to
make that same mistake again?

31:05.100 --> 31:08.270
♪ It's true ♪

31:07.500 --> 31:09.220
Dad, I stayed three years ago,

31:08.900 --> 31:12.180
♪ I miss you ♪

31:09.220 --> 31:10.910
and I've never regretted it.

31:11.460 --> 31:12.870
I only had a tiny bit of regret.

31:12.200 --> 31:18.440
♪ Hope the night brings me to you ♪

31:12.870 --> 31:14.830
But how could you call my regret

31:14.830 --> 31:16.220
a blessing?

31:19.660 --> 31:22.300
♪ And I also know ♪

31:22.900 --> 31:29.240
♪ The night will pass
and I have to part with you ♪

31:29.970 --> 31:38.150
♪ It's hard to accept but true ♪

32:00.300 --> 32:02.250
♪ It's true ♪

32:04.170 --> 32:06.360
♪ I loved you ♪

32:04.340 --> 32:05.600
No matter what you say,

32:06.310 --> 32:07.460
I still don't agree.

32:06.780 --> 32:12.860
♪ Hope the dream brings me to you ♪

32:09.880 --> 32:11.710
But I know I can't control you.

32:14.650 --> 32:16.610
♪ And I also know ♪

32:16.630 --> 32:22.800
♪ The dreams are false
and I should forget you ♪

32:23.220 --> 32:23.910
Uncle.

32:24.150 --> 32:34.150
♪ It's hard to accept but true ♪

33:06.590 --> 33:07.460
Dad,

33:07.980 --> 33:10.110
do we really have to move?

33:10.390 --> 33:11.540
I've counted.

33:11.910 --> 33:14.830
It's 30 steps per floor.

33:15.110 --> 33:16.870
If you want to go up or down,

33:16.980 --> 33:18.300
you can call me.

33:18.630 --> 33:20.020
I'll help you walk.

33:20.150 --> 33:22.670
That way, your leg won't hurt.

33:23.540 --> 33:24.910
I don't want to move.

33:25.150 --> 33:27.150
I can't bear to leave everyone here.

33:27.950 --> 33:29.260
Xiu, stop talking.

33:29.500 --> 33:30.910
It's not about your dad's leg.

33:30.910 --> 33:32.710
He's heartbroken, understand?

33:41.020 --> 33:42.630
Living at school is so convenient.

33:42.630 --> 33:43.780
Why did you have to move out?

33:43.780 --> 33:44.870
What a hassle.

33:45.260 --> 33:46.740
Xiu didn't tell you?

33:46.740 --> 33:48.740
The dorm shuts the lights off
at a certain time.

33:48.740 --> 33:50.590
She can only draw by a desk lamp,

33:50.700 --> 33:51.540
you know?

33:51.540 --> 33:52.150
Dad, Mom,

33:52.150 --> 33:53.500
I've redesigned our rooms.

33:53.500 --> 33:54.500
Go take a look.

34:02.630 --> 34:03.460
Dad? Mom?

34:04.940 --> 34:06.380
Why are you here?

34:08.639 --> 34:10.500
I'm taking your dad for a follow-up
at the hospital.

34:10.500 --> 34:12.330
We were passing by, so we came to see you.

34:12.330 --> 34:14.060
You became a regular employee?

34:17.020 --> 34:17.949
Actually,

34:17.969 --> 34:19.719
Shiyuan Real Estate is quite good.

34:19.719 --> 34:22.620
Your cousin wanted to work there before
but couldn't get in.

34:22.620 --> 34:24.750
I know. Let me walk you two to get a taxi.

35:11.730 --> 35:13.620
You ordered
all this fried chicken and fries,

35:13.620 --> 35:14.750
and you're just leaving it out here?

35:14.750 --> 35:16.410
At least take it inside to eat.

35:17.830 --> 35:18.890
And these flowers.

35:19.180 --> 35:20.060
If you leave them like this,

35:20.060 --> 35:21.120
they'll wilt soon.

35:39.830 --> 35:41.270
The onion bulbs fell on the floor,

35:41.270 --> 35:43.730
and you didn't even come out
to clean them up.

37:22.710 --> 37:24.770
The drainpipe under the upstairs sink
is broken.

37:24.770 --> 37:26.690
If you don't want the loft to flood,

37:26.690 --> 37:27.890
come up and fix it now.

37:28.500 --> 37:30.100
There are spare pipes
in the living room cabinet.

37:30.100 --> 37:31.460
You can replace it yourself.

37:31.460 --> 37:32.060
No.

37:33.020 --> 37:33.820
My hand hurts.

38:23.910 --> 38:25.830
Didn't we just replace the pipe
a few months ago?

38:25.830 --> 38:27.090
Why is it broken again?

38:27.500 --> 38:28.500
See for yourself.

38:44.390 --> 38:45.560
Are you messing with me?

38:45.560 --> 38:47.580
If I hadn't resorted to
such a dirty trick,

38:47.580 --> 38:50.660
you would've stayed in bed
until the Design Competition.

38:50.660 --> 38:51.660
I would not.

38:55.580 --> 38:57.620
But you were right about one thing—

38:58.270 --> 38:59.230
not telling my parents

38:59.230 --> 39:00.620
about changing jobs

39:01.450 --> 39:03.050
was like setting a time bomb.

39:03.990 --> 39:05.590
But you defused it yourself.

39:05.950 --> 39:08.610
Aren't you still standing here
perfectly fine?

39:10.790 --> 39:11.710
I have a way

39:11.870 --> 39:14.230
to help you forget everything temporarily.

39:14.230 --> 39:14.830
Wait here.

39:21.000 --> 39:21.910
Watch out.

39:21.910 --> 39:23.240
You're taller than I am.

39:27.570 --> 39:30.450
What's that method you mentioned?

39:40.640 --> 39:42.100
It really is a good method.

39:43.460 --> 39:44.140
Let's do it.

39:53.410 --> 39:57.960
♪ Close your eyes for me ♪

39:59.480 --> 40:01.650
♪ Don't rush to wake up ♪

40:02.130 --> 40:05.350
♪ Before the night ends ♪

40:06.750 --> 40:07.500
Here.

40:08.230 --> 40:13.550
♪ Will you stay with me? ♪

40:14.470 --> 40:16.470
♪ I won't search for ♪

40:17.270 --> 40:20.080
♪ The reason we met ♪

40:21.890 --> 40:27.420
♪ The city gradually turns pale
outside the window ♪

40:28.430 --> 40:29.750
The dimensions are wrong.

40:28.800 --> 40:30.920
♪ The stars twinkle ♪

40:29.980 --> 40:31.840
You made the same mistake before.

40:31.910 --> 40:35.920
♪ I've quieted down ♪

40:37.480 --> 40:39.320
♪ Escape the world ♪

40:39.340 --> 40:40.940
♪ Forget all things ♪

40:40.980 --> 40:44.340
♪ And fall down a long, romantic dream ♪

40:44.360 --> 40:46.670
♪ Just you and me ♪

40:47.360 --> 40:49.680
♪ Under moonlight ♪

40:52.040 --> 40:54.610
♪ Briefly, beyond the clamor ♪

40:54.650 --> 40:56.550
♪ Getting closer to you secretly ♪

40:56.570 --> 41:00.420
♪ Clinging to that trace of unknown joy ♪

41:00.810 --> 41:04.820
♪ Oh, special night ♪

41:08.050 --> 41:12.320
♪ We will meet tomorrow ♪

41:13.680 --> 41:15.290
♪ I know ♪

41:15.650 --> 41:19.640
♪ Oh, special night ♪

41:22.910 --> 41:26.830
♪ Oh, special night ♪

41:48.060 --> 41:48.860
Did you see it?

41:49.580 --> 41:50.230
How is it?

41:50.580 --> 41:51.230
Not bad.

41:51.950 --> 41:52.750
How about you?

41:54.910 --> 41:55.640
Pretty good.

42:00.100 --> 42:01.430
I've figured it out now.

42:01.790 --> 42:03.580
There's only one shortcut

42:04.060 --> 42:05.390
to solving everything—

42:05.790 --> 42:06.790
and that is to win.

42:08.430 --> 42:09.060
Win?

42:11.830 --> 42:12.790
Something that difficult,

42:12.790 --> 42:14.250
and you call it a shortcut?

42:16.910 --> 42:18.620
Though it's difficult,

42:19.260 --> 42:21.520
it can solve a lot of problems
all at once.

42:21.830 --> 42:22.460
Look,

42:22.950 --> 42:24.580
if we win this competition,

42:24.910 --> 42:26.710
I can become a regular employee.

42:26.870 --> 42:28.310
Once I become a regular employee,
I can get a raise

42:28.310 --> 42:30.390
and work on
the follow-up project implementation.

42:30.390 --> 42:31.140
When the project is implemented,

42:31.140 --> 42:33.070
I'll have a small accomplishment.

42:33.430 --> 42:34.390
Then, at that time,
no matter how my father...

42:34.390 --> 42:35.320
Hold on, hold on.

42:37.500 --> 42:39.020
You haven't "figured things out."

42:39.020 --> 42:40.550
You're clearly pushing me.

42:43.280 --> 42:44.550
I wouldn't dare.

42:48.350 --> 42:49.620
They should be out at their stalls now.

42:49.620 --> 42:50.180
Let's go, Mr. Xiao.

42:50.180 --> 42:51.360
Let's go grab some breakfast.

42:51.360 --> 42:52.290
What's the rush?

42:53.500 --> 42:54.460
I'm in a rush.

42:54.460 --> 42:56.140
I have to come back and draw the next one.

42:56.140 --> 42:57.500
Come on, get moving. Let's go.
